      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a resident of the state of Sikkim.\n1. The applicant with 40% and above disability is eligible for the scheme.\n1. The applicant should belong to Below Poverty Line (BPL) household.\n1. The applicant should not be covered under Indira Gandhi National Disability Pension Scheme (IGNDPS).\n1. The applicant should have opened the Bank Account under “Pradhan Mantri Jan Dhan Yojana”.\n\n",
